narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Only the best things to say about this course; a real highlight of my semester, and a great experience reading these texts.
This class is a lot different than L1 or L2. It is just translate texts at home and go over them in class. It is not easy at all. Be prepared to work in this class.

Anyone considering this class should keep in mind that the translations take a significant amount of time to complete. That being said, the material is interesting and it is very satisfying when you complete a translation.
